      "comment": "DOLLY DAWN (2) filled a minor placing last start at this track behind Canya Paprika (17.69) in a Grade 5. Has the pace to be prominent. Good form should continue. RED BROOK (1) recorded a 5.5 lengths second in a Grade 4 last time 17.86 at this track and trip and also jumping from the same draw. Harder here but will be in this for a long way. KINGSBRAE MAGGIE (7) was strongly fancied last time but finished third (17.76), beaten 6 lengths. Hard to beat again. REMISSION RUN (4) is worth including after a top-three finish at this track and distance most recently.",
